videos.description: Quinton Flowers throws a short pass to D'Ernest Johnson who jukes a defender and scampers for 25 yards.
videos.headline: USF's Johnson makes move for big gain

videos.description: Texas Tech Nic Shimonek connects with Keke Coutee down the sideline for 37 yards in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Shimonek heaves long ball to Coutee for Red Raiders

videos.description: Nic Shimonek rolls out and throws a five-yard touchdown to Keke Coutee in the back of the end zone.
videos.headline: Shimonek finds Coutee open for Texas Tech TD

videos.description: Cameron Batson has to adjust on a broken flea-flicker and scrambles all the way to the two-yard line.
videos.headline: Batson dodges multiple tackles on broken play for Texas Tech

videos.description: Nic Shimonek's pass is tipped twice and intercepted by South Florida's Jaymon Thomas who returns it 18 yards.
videos.headline: Shimonek picked off in end zone

videos.description: Quinton Flowers ties it up with a 21-yard touchdown to Trye McCants late in the 2nd quarter for the Bulls.
videos.headline: Flowers fires to McCants for a tying USF TD

videos.description: Nic Shimonek takes advantage of the free play and finds Dylan Cantrell for a three-yard touchdown pass in the corner.
videos.headline: Cantrell shrugs off defender for Red Raider TD

videos.description: Quinton Flowers gives Darnell Salomon space with a pump fake and lobs an easy 17-yard touchdown to his receiver to tie the game at 17.
videos.headline: Flowers connects with Salomon for Bulls TD

videos.description: Tre King bounces off his lineman and cuts inside for a four-yard rushing touchdown to give Texas Tech a 7-point lead.
videos.headline: King dives in for Texas Tech TD

videos.description: Quinton Flowers connects with Marquez Valdes-Scantling on a huge 43-yard gain for the Bulls.
videos.headline: Flowers launches deep ball to Valdes-Scantling for USF

videos.description: Quinton Flowers takes it 29 yards on the QB keeper down the sideline and tacks on an extra 15 yards on a late hit from Texas Tech's Vaughnte Dorsey.
videos.headline: Flowers scrambles for huge gain on 4th down

videos.description: Texas Tech's defense delivers another big stop on 4th down with South Florida on the one-yard line in the 4th quarter.
videos.headline: Tice stuffed at the goal line by Texas Tech on 4th down

videos.description: Quinton Flowers looks to pass then takes it to the corner for the five-yard rushing touchdown to tie it at 24.
videos.headline: Flowers races to the end zone to tie it for the Bulls

videos.description: Quinton Flowers finds Marquez Valdes-Scantling wide open on a 64-yard touchdown pass to put the Bulls up 30-27 late in the 4th quarter.
videos.headline: Flowers flings huge TD pass to Valdes-Scantling

videos.description: Keke Coutee dives to make a 28-yard catch from Nic Shimonek to get the Red Raiders into USF territory.
videos.headline: Coutee makes diving grab for Texas Tech

videos.description: Nic Shimonek connects with a wide open T.J. Vasher on a 25-yard touchdown pass to put Texas Tech back on top 34-31.
videos.headline: Vasher left wide open in end zone for TD

videos.description: Quinton Flowers throws a perfect 26-yard touchdown pass to Tyre McCants to give South Florida a 38-34 lead with 16 seconds left in the game.
videos.headline: USF takes late lead with McCants TD

videos.description: South Florida head coach Charlie Strong reflects on his team's 10-win season and cuts the interview short due to a Gatorade bath.
videos.headline: Strong doused with Gatorade
